Package: colourgen
Title: One Colour Palette Interface to rule them all
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Caleb", "Jenkins", email = "calebajenkins@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a single, consistent interface for generating colour palettes in R.
    Plot previewing and actual hex colors are the main features here.
